
// Adds nodes retrieved from the specified arguments to the current node's children. The [add] slot appends nodes obtained from [get-nodes] expressions pointing to [order] and [direction] within [.arguments]. This effectively integrates these nodes into the current node's hierarchy.
add:x:./*/data.read
   get-nodes:x:@.arguments/*/order
   get-nodes:x:@.arguments/*/direction
